<p>Welcome <%= @resource.first_name %>!</p>

<p>We have added your contact information to our notifier. When you get mail or a guest arrives for you, our team will let you know at the contact information we have stored for you. Currently, that is:</p>

<p>Name: <%= @resource.first_name %> <%= @resource.last_name %><br />
<% if @resource.company_name %>
Company: <%= @resource.company_name %><br />
<% end %>
Email: <%= @resource.email %><br />
<% if @resource.phone_number %>
Telephone: <%= @resource.phone_number %><br />
<% end %>
</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password here', edit_password_url(@resource, :reset_password_token => @resource.reset_password_token) %></p>

<p>Please check that this information is up to date. If it is not, we invite you to update it and other notification preferences <%= link_to 'here', edit_password_url(@resource) %>.</p>

Thanks!

<p>The XTeam</p>
